title: ‘An Honor for Me’: U.S. Junior Champion Darren Parham Joins Hagens Berman Axeon
content:
Hot Tubes alumni steps up to prestigious development team for its first year associated to WorldTour squad Jayco-AlUla.

Read the full article at ‘An Honor for Me’: U.S. Junior Champion Darren Parham Joins Hagens Berman Axeon on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
